cs.CL, cs.SD, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with learning neural network embeddings for speech waveforms without linguistic transcriptions.
- cs.SD (Sound) is also likely as the paper deals with speech waveforms and their embeddings.
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is relevant as the paper also explores learning embeddings for natural images.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the use of neural network models for learning embeddings.
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is relevant as the paper deals with both speech and image data.
